com.verisign.epp.codec.suggestion
Interface EPPSuggestionConstants

public interface EPPSuggestionConstants

Title: EPPSuggestionConstants Description: This interface defines constants to be used when processing the language and key elements from the EPP Suggestion INFO command. It also includes constants which identify the expected values for the language element. Copyright: Copyright (c) 2008 Company: VeriSign

Version:
1.0, Oct 21, 2008
Author:
psitowitz
